569
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:44,220
it'll be difficult for us to win.

570
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:47,340
We mustn't let Di Ziyuan arrive at the borders.

571
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:48,460
Yes, Your Highness.

572
