576
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:11,740
If so, Anle is...

577
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:14,220
I'll back her up.

578
00:34:14,220 --> 00:34:14,860
Wen Shuo,

579
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:15,980
